articles.author: The Associated Press
articles.title: Elon Musk accuses Australia of censorship after court bans violent video - NBC News
articles.description: Tech billionaire Elon Musk accused Australia of censorship after an Australian judge ruled that his social media platform X must block users worldwide from accessing video of a bishop being stabbed in a Sydney church.
